org.hsqldb
Class Profile

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--org.hsqldb.Profile
public class Profile
extends java.lang.Object

This class is used to test and profile HSQL Database Engine. Before it can be used, the source code of the database must be changed using CodeSwitcher, then compiled, then the test program must be run, and at the end the static function listUnvisited must be called. This will list all not visited lines and it will print out the top 20 lines with the most visits, the longest run and the longest run per call.

This class is generic can be used to profile also other programs.
